parts.text: A cute clay doll monkey with soft, hand-molded clay texture and subtle thumbprint marks, a matte finish, sits on a miniature clay chair. The monkey has bright orange fur and black bead eyes, a playful expression on its face as its tiny clay fingers hold a clay banana, taking a bite. The chair is also made of clay, with a slightly textured, matte surface. The background is a simple, blurred miniature set with clay details. The scene is brightly lit with studio lighting, and a shallow depth of field keeps the monkey and banana in sharp focus.
